modName: Lanterns of Skyrim- All in one- Realistic Kilo Preset
summary: This is my preset for Lanterns in Skyrim - All in one mod. I found some presets that doesn\'t look quite naturally, so I tried to make my own that will look more realistic while still maintaining a decent level of light. It does also contain Flicker effect.
